<p>‚Äú<a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-9.7/">iPad</a> is the perfect tool for teaching in new and compelling ways, and our <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-9.7/">iPad</a> results were especially strong in the US education market, where sales were up 32 percent year over year to over one million units.‚Äù</p>

<p>The lower cost <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-9.7/">iPad</a> which was launched earlier this year replaced the <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-9.7/">iPad</a> Air 2 and has a 9.7‚Äù screen. The <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-9.7/">iPad</a> mini 4 is still on sale and it‚Äôs form makes it attractive for everyday tasks were the iPhone is not large enough. The <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-9.7/">iPad</a> has an A9 chip which supports multitasking which greatly increases productivity, and picture in picture.</p>

