<p>The <a href="https://www.apple.com/ipad-pro/">iPad Pro</a> now has the A10X processor which is made using a 10nm manufacturing process making it one of the most advanced processors on the planet with 40% faster graphics and 30% faster CPU performance. It offers 6 cores and is more powerful than many desktop / laptop processors. Combine this with the Apple pencil and you have a great all round device that can replace most laptops.</p>

